<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>An exceptionally rare ginger fur seal pup has been spotted in the Sea of Okhotsk in Russia.</p>

<p>The pinniped stands out from the rest of its colony with its colouring, blue eyes and pink flippers.</p>

<p>Experts say the chances of such a partial albino birth are one in 100,000 and there is a risk of rejection by the rookery.</p>

